    <div class="alpheios-lex-entry" lemma-id="n9728" body-key="α">
          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">χώομαι</span></b>  (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">χέω</span>), imp. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">χώεο</span>, ipf.
            <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">χώετο</span>, aor. (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἐ</span>)<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">χώσατο</span>, subj. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">χώσεται</span>, part. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">-άμενος</span>: <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">be agitated, troubled, angered;</span>
