          w. dat. of the person, <i><span class="en">Il. 1.80</span></i>, <i><span class="en">Il. 9.555</span></i>; causal gen. of thing or person,
            <i><span class="en">Il. 1.429</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
